<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="A few bits about me and this blog"
  pubDate={new Date("October 22 2024")}
  heroImage={photo}
>
  <p>My name is Leo. I'm based in the beautiful city Augsburg, Germany.</p>

  <p>
    I am a software engineer, working at <a href="https://www.peerigon.com/en/"
      >Peerigon</a
    > since 2017. Previously I had the pleasure to work for a startup in Bogotá,
