    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/leonhardmelzer/"
      >professional profile on LinkedIn</a
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>Colophon</h2>

  <p>
    This blog is built on top of the fantastic <a href="https://astro.build/"
      >Astro</a
    > and their blog starter. It's continously built by <a
      href="https://www.netlify.com/">Netlify</a
    >. The branding (logo, color and font suggestions) was made by
    <a href="https://www.logology.co/">Logology</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    I'm happy about feedback. Feel free to <a
      href="https://github.com/leomelzer/write-hike">open an issue on GitHub</a
    > or contact me at <a href="mailto:leonhard.melzer@gmail.com"
